## REQ-BFF-003: JWT Authentication Forwarding

### Scenario: Standard JWT forwarding via operationHeaders
```gherkin
Given a source with operationHeaders configured
  And Authorization header uses {context.jwt} placeholder
When a GraphQL request is made with Authorization header
Then the REST API call includes the forwarded JWT token
```

### Scenario: Request ID forwarding
```gherkin
Given a source with X-Request-ID in operationHeaders
When a GraphQL request includes X-Request-ID header
Then the REST API call includes the same request ID
```

